==生物多樣性==
[[File:Maldivesfish2.jpg|thumb]]是豐富地海洋生物主要棲息地，容易吸引{{le|生物勘測|Bioprospecting}}者前來破壞。目前許多珊瑚礁面臨過度開發的情況；其威脅通常包括開採珊瑚、使用{{le|氰化物捕鱼|cyanide fishing|氰化物}}或[[爆破捕魚|爆破]]等方式捕魚、以及單純[[過度捕魚|過度捕魚]]等。]]

過度開發是全球[[生物多樣性|生物多樣性]]的主要威脅之一。<ref name=Wilcoveetal />其他威脅包括環境[[污染|污染]]、[[外來物種|外來物種]]引進或[[入侵物種|入侵]]、[[棲息地零碎化|棲息地零碎化]]、[[棲息地破壞|棲息地破壞]]<ref name=Wilcoveetal />、[[雜交種|雜交失控]]<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1146/annurev.ecolsys.27.1.83 | title = Extinction by Hybridization and Introgression | year = 1996 | last1 = Rhymer | first1 = Judith M. | last2 = Simberloff | first2 = Daniel | journal = Annual Review of Ecology and Systematics | volume = 27 | pages = 83–109 | jstor = 2097230 }}</ref>、[[全球暖化|全球暖化]] <ref name = "Kannan2009">{{cite journal
 | last1 = Kannan | first1 = R.  | last2 =James | first2 = D. A.
 | title = Effects of climate change on global biodiversity: a review of key literature
 | journal = Tropical Ecology | volume = 50 | issue = 1 | pages = 31–39
 | publisher = | location = | date = 2009 | issn = 0564-3295
 | url = http://www.tropecol.com/pdf/open/PDF_50_1/05Kannan.pdf
 | accessdate = 2014-05-21}}</ref>、[[海洋酸化|海洋酸化]] <ref name=Mora>{{cite journal |last1=Mora |first1=C.|title=Biotic and Human Vulnerability to Projected Changes in Ocean Biogeochemistry over the 21st Century |journal=PLoS Biology |volume=11 |pages=e1001682 |year=2013 |doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.1001682|display-authors=etal |pmid=24143135 |pmc=3797030}}</ref>、以及許多因[[人口過多|人口過多]]造成的因素。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Dumont | first1 = E. | year = 2012 | title = Estimated impact of global population growth on future wilderness extent. | url = http://www.earth-syst-dynam-discuss.net/3/433/2012/esdd-3-433-2012.pdf | format = PDF | journal = Earth System Dynamics Discussions | volume = 3 | pages = 433–452 | doi = 10.5194/esdd-3-433-2012 | bibcode = 2012ESDD....3..433D | author =  | access-date = 2016-08-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171122200054/https://www.earth-syst-dynam-discuss.net/3/433/2012/esdd-3-433-2012.pdf | archive-date = 2017-11-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>


藥物開發與藥材資源的使用等健康主要問題，成為威脅生物多樣性中的一個要點。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gmo-compass.org/eng/glossary/177.molecular_pharming.html |date=2006 |title=Molecular Pharming |work=GMO Compass |accessdate=November 5, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090929121107/http://www.gmo-compass.org/eng/glossary/177.molecular_pharming.html |archivedate=2009年9月29日 }}</ref>不管是直接或間接[[天然產物|天然產物]]藥品，從生物當來源的比例顯著的增加，其中海洋生態系統的生物特別深入其中。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Roopesh |first=J. |year=2008 |title=Marine organisms: Potential Source for Drug Discovery |journal=Current Science |volume=94 |issue=3 |pages=292 |doi= |url=http://documents.mx/documents/marine-organisms-potential-source-for-drug-discovery.html |display-authors=etal |author= |access-date=2016-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170329012926/http://documents.mx/documents/marine-organisms-potential-source-for-drug-discovery.html |archive-date=2017-03-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>但是在無管控或是不當{{le|生物勘測|Bioprospecting}}會導致過度開發現象，使生態系統退化與生物多樣性降低。<ref name = "Dhillion">{{cite journal | title = Bioprospecting: Effects on Environment and Development | journal = {{le|人類環境雜志|AMBIO: A Journal of the Human Environment|AMBIO}} | date = September 2002 | first = S. S. | last = Dhillion |author2=Svarstad, H. |author3=Amundsen, C. |author4=Bugge, H. C. | volume = 31 | issue = 6 | pages = 491–493 | id = | jstor = 4315292 | doi=10.1639/0044-7447(2002)031[0491:beoead]2.0.co;2 | pmid=12436849}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last=Cole |first=Andrew |year=2005 |title=Looking for new compounds in sea is endangering ecosystem |journal=[[British_Medical_Journal|BMJ]] |volume=330 |issue=7504 |pages=1350 |doi=10.1136/bmj.330.7504.1350-d }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cohabnet.org/en_issue4.htm |title=COHAB Initiative - on Natural Products and Medicinal Resources |publisher=Cohabnet.org |accessdate=2009-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025100247/http://cohabnet.org/en_issue4.htm |archive-date=2017-10-25 |dead-url=